cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with human pose estimation using deep convolutional neural networks. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a CRF-CNN framework for modeling structural information in a probabilistic way. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with integrating structural information effectively in neural networks. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with human pose estimation, which is a multimedia-related problem. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possible category as the paper proposes a neural network implementation of end-to-end learning CRF-CNN.
